Use the standard library
This is how to count_nums of arr:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this arr's length times:
      When item i in arr is more than 0, then:
         Increase count
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is count
Now you know

>>> count_nums of []
0
>>> count_nums of [-1, 11, -11]
1
>>> count_nums of [1, 1, 2]
3